    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vessels, usually with a handle and a stopper, used to serve condiments; generally of glass and often made in sets of two or more.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
